2. \f4\u-10179?\u-9040?\f2  \f0 Your Exact Funding Stack (Tailored to You)\par
You\f2\rquote\f0 re not a single-product startup. You\f2\rquote\f0 re building:\par
Property marketplace\par
EdTech platform\par
AI communication layer\par
\f4\u-10179?\u-9143?\f2  \f0 That\f2\rquote\f0 s powerful if positioned correctly.\par
