3. \f1\u-10178?\u-8736?\f2  \f0 Pitch Deck Structure (SA Investor-Ready)\par
Keep it tight (10\f2\endash 12 slides max):\par
1. Problem\par
Schools lack digital communication\par
Property market is fragmented in townships\par
2. Solution\par
Unified platform:\par
Property marketplace\par
EdTech delivery\par
AI communication (multi-language)\par
3. Market Opportunity\par
Public schools in SA (~25,000+)\par
Informal + township property market\par
4. Product\par
Demo screenshots\par
MVP walkthrough\par
5. Business Model\par
Listings (freemium \f3\u8594?\f2  \f0 paid)\par
School subscriptions\par
Government licensing\par
6. Traction\par
Users / pilots / partnerships\par
7. Go-To-Market\par
Direct to schools\par
Municipal partnerships\par
Community ambassadors\par
8. Competitive Advantage\par
Local language AI\par
Offline-first capability\par
Public-sector alignment\par
9. Financials\par
BasIc projections (3 years)\par
10. Team\par
You (technical + vision)\par
11. Ask\par
Amount + use of funds\par
4. \f1\u-10178?\u-8706?\f2  \f0 Step-by-Step Tender-Winning Strategy\par
This is where most fail. Here\f2\rquote\f0 s the real play:\par
STEP 1 \f2\emdash  Don\rquote t chase big tenders first\par
Start with:\par
RFQs (Request for Quotations)\par
Small contracts (<R500K)\par
STEP 2 \emdash  Build a \ldblquote Tender-Ready Profile\rdblquote\par
You need:\par
Company profile (clean PDF)\par
Past work (even pilot projects)\par
Clear service offering\par
STEP 3 \emdash  Partner Up (CRITICAL)\par
If you lack experience:\par
\f4\u-10179?\u-9143?\f2  \f0 Partner with:\par
Existing IT companies\par
NGOs\par
Consultants\par
STEP 4 \f2\emdash  Price strategically\par
Don\rquote t underprice blindly\par
Show VALUE (training + support + rollout)\par
STEP 5 \emdash  Follow up aggressively\par
Call after submission:\par
\ldblquote We submitted proposal ref X, just confirming evaluation timelines.\rdblquote\par
STEP 6 \emdash  Use losses as leverage\par
Ask:\par
\ldblquote Where did we fall short?\rdblquote\par
Refine. Reapply.\par
5. \f1\u9888?\u-497?\f2  \f0 Hard Truth (Strategic Insight)\par
In South Africa:\par
Funding follows traction\par
Traction comes from relationships + pilots\par
Tenders favor credibility + compliance\par
\f4\u-10179?\u-9143?\f2  \f0 Translation:\par
You win by being visible + active in the ecosystem, not just \f2\ldblquote\f0 applying online.\f2\rdblquote\f0\par
If you want next level execution:\par
I can:\par
Build your actual pitch deck (content + slides)\par
Draft your CSD + tender profile pack\par
Or design your first school pilot rollout strategy\par
Just tell me:\par
\f4\u-10179?\u-9143?\f2  \ldblquote\f0 Build the deck\f2\rdblquote  \f0 or \f2\ldblquote\f0 Pilot rollout plan\f2\rdblquote\f0\lang9\par
